title: She Used To Be  My Sugar Baby
itunes:title: She Used To Be  My Sugar Baby
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley, I am a 49 year old retired businessman. I had a start-up in the early 2000s that did very well and I sold it in a multi-million-dollar deal. I make the majority of my income now from my real estate investments. That’s how I met my 27 year old fiancé. She was renting one of my houses and after three months of her living there, we had sex and I started taking care of her in every way. Here’s why…..............
